ActFederal Real Property and Federal Immovables Act
SubjectTransfer to BC residual interest - Maa-nulth First Nations
PrecisOrder transferring to British Columbia the administration and control of the entire residual interest, if any, of Canada in former federal lands, including Maa-nulth First Nations Reserve lands, which will become Maa-nulth First Nation Lands.
